<%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

<section id="contact">
    <div class="container py-4">
        <div class="p-5 mb-4 bg-body-tertiary rounded-3">
          <div class="container-fluid py-5">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Join Our Community</h1>
            <p class="col-md-12 fs-5">
                We believe that game development is a collaborative endeavor, 
                and that's why we've built a thriving community of like-minded individuals who share 
                our passion for games. Join us on dribble and meet up to connect with fellow 
                developers, share your projects, and stay updated on the latest news and events in the 
                world of game development. Together, we can unlock the full potential of our creativity 
                and create games that inspire and entertain players around the world.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="row align-items-md-stretch">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="h-100 p-5 text-bg-dark rounded-3">
              <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
              <p>
                Have questions, feedback, or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you! 
                Feel free to reach out to us at sombadennis@gmail.com or use our contact form below. 
                Whether you're looking for advice on a specific aspect of game development or just want to 
                say hello, we're here to help.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="h-100 p-5 bg-body-tertiary border rounded-3">
              <h2>Explore More</h2>
              <p>
                Ready to dive deeper into the world of game development? Check out some of our popular 
                tutorials or browse our homepage for more content on game development. 
                Whether you're a hobbyist, indie developer, or aspiring professional, there's something 
                for everyone at Dennis Blog.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="p-5 mb-4 bg-body-tertiary rounded-3 mt-5">
            <div class="container-fluid py-5">
              <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Contact Us</h1>

              <form>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1" class="form-label">Full Name</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="fullName" placeholder="Mike Omolo">
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1" class="form-label">Email address</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlInput1" placeholder="name@example.com">
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1" class="form-label">Your Message</label>
                    <textarea class="form-control" id="yourMessage" rows="3"></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
              </form> 
            </div>
          </div>
    </div>
</section>
<%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>